name: Jess Sheldon
text: The pizza was cooked perfectly. Drew offered exceptional customer service. Extremely polite!

text: great service here. even reminded what i ordered last time so i could order it again. only negative would be that the pan crust needs to.be cooked a lil more to get that texture and.flavor like.the old school pan pizzaas had

text: Had a horrible experience on 11-22-19.  First, I ordered by phone and was routed to a strange call center instead of the actual store.  That was annoying.  However, I got the order in and was told "15 minutes".  I showed up at the store â€¦More

name: Sarah Welch
text: I met my parents in the parking lot both of us from out of town. The pizza didnt take very long to make and everything tasted great. Inside dinning would have been nice but oh well. :)

text: All the stuff is frozen and to greased.

name: Andrea Schumann
text: Pizza Hut has the best pan pizza crust and the best bread sticks and the most awesome brownie dessert

name: Frankie Sanchez
text: Quick service,  tasteful food and friendly staff member.. got take out and left a tip for the one guy working and was very much appreciated... dont forget it is ok to tip on carryout also.

name: Mike Broadbent
text: I made an error regarding the time to be delivered  when placing my order online, so no one was home when the delivery took place. Although this was definitely my error the staff at this location were extremely pleasant and actually remade my order just so I wouldn't have to eat cold food! Top notch professional service!

name: Darla Albert
text: Went to the buffet and EVERYTHING was empty including salad bar and there was so many people there it was such a waste. All we got was drinks and they charged for such horrible service. So bad even the people behind us said it was bad when they got there to me when they seen us leaving. Don't waste your time.

name: Mark Wilkes
text: The guy running the store tonight was amazing.  Deserves a raise

text:
I ordered a Veggie pizza and found meat pieces on it. Though, they offered me another one, I was not in a mood to eat pizza any more today.
Thanks, they are giving me credit, but I am not at all happy today.
